        "answer": "The fused batched MoE layer in vLLM returns the activations as a tensor of shape (num_experts, max_tokens, K), where:\n\n- `num_experts` is the number of experts.\n- `max_tokens` is the maximum number of tokens that can be processed with the expert.\n- `K` is the token dimension.\n\nThis format is used when the All2All Dispatch is set to batched mode, and the activations are grouped across experts for efficient inference."
